  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK472">
<l>olva taṟiva taṟintataṉ kaṭṭaṅkic</l>
<l>celvārkkuc cellāta til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing which may not be accomplished by those who, before they attack (an enemy), make themselves acquainted with their own ability, and with whatever else is (needful) to be known, and apply themselves wholly to their object.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
